:"If this method is present in the delegate, it must return a new instance of a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view dedicated to display the callout. The returned view will be configured by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If this method is absent from the delegate, or if it returns "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", a standard,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"two-line, bubble-like callout view is displayed by default."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"text":"Related examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts, learn how to customize an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object’s ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:calloutviewforannotation:"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a callout view to display for the given annotation."}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L890","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","title":"mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutView":{"title":"MLNCalloutView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutview","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol for a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclass that displays information about a selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation near that annotation."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNCalloutView"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapViewDelegate"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","title":"MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"type":"text",